<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation and Invoice</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .booking-details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Booking Confirmation and Invoice</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="booking-details">
            <p>Dear {{ customerName }},</p>
            <p>Thank you for booking with us!</p>
            <p>Here are your booking details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Number of Nights: {{ numberOfNights }}</li>
                <li>Price per Night: ${{ pricePerNight }}</li>
                <li>Total Price Paid: ${{ totalPrice }}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Hotel Dashboard Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
